udy, you will read a short review ab...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Welcome! Thank you for your interest in our study. In this study, you will read a short review about a charity organization and answer several questions about it. Your responses will be used for academic research purposes only. There are no right or wrong answers. Please read all information carefully and answer honestly.\n\nThis study will take about 2-5 minutes to complete.\n<br><br>By clicking \u201cNext,\u201d you confirm that you are at least 18 years old and consent to participate in this study.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Introduction","QuestionID":"QID1","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Welcome! Thank you for your interest in our study. In this study, you will read a short review ab...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6M33amoAOtOJoj4","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID10","SecondaryAttribute":"To what extent did the review contain details?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"To what extent did the review contain details?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Detail","QuestionID":"QID10","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAHR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","LabelPosition":"BELOW"},"QuestionDescription":"To what extent did the review contain details?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Not at all detailed"},"2":{"Display":"Slightly detailed"},"3":{"Display":"Moderately detailed"},"4":{"Display":"Very detailed"},"5":{"Display":"Extremely detailed"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2,3,4,5],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":6,"Next